text:
Oops, looks like we ran out of spray...
We were having so much fun cleaning the windows...

Haha...
Maybe we were playing around too much.

Mmm... It's a shame we ran out halfway through,
I wanted to finish cleaning them all...

...Hey, since I came here on my scooter today,
should I go buy some?

This window cleaning spray,
isn't it available at the nearby drugstore?

Oh! If that's the case, I'll go with you~!
I don't want to leave you to go alone~

It's fine, it's fine.
I'll go quickly and come back!
